wn.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c95411ed7d361d794bb79342964114473fbe46","tid":1242321,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:07:36.000Z","msg":"追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5919c5b63b1f27f0f71b67b620b1d323f6a74830","tid":1242321,"uid":52946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:00:32.000Z","msg":"我相信好快會咁上下 因為呢幾星期發生既事 又無乜野改變到香港 大陸一定會諗方法 第一樣就係教育洗腦 等以後既青年人唔敢/唔會上街 之後就慢慢推返以前停左既野出黎 等大家過左倒氣慢慢又玩返佢地依家做緊既野<br />\n所以呢個星期一定要逼到政府要聽民意做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真普選還政於民 真港人治港 釋放所有民運政治比捕義士 撤回條例 林鄭下台  廢除功能組別等"},{"pid":"1eaf3b9dfc4a882aee73da80eb55c89b600ed9c7","tid":1242321,"uid":245126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:16:08.000Z","msg":"好恐怖呀屌"},{"pid":"074a1ec6b847f09e577f9b2fbef3a5eadbfe8dc2","tid":1242321,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c885f53bd69bbf64dd0b2cc09d8215d1b2f528b","tid":1242321,"uid":221827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:23:26.000Z","msg":"關手機乜撚嘢事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d7df82db7cfdb7e8178f15bddefd60611c52c7","tid":1242321,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:27:14.000Z","msg":"去錯台？"},{"pid":"1240a57d69bef24010d54a158b8f716d3925fdad","tid":1242321,"uid":258236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9d7df82db7cfdb7e8178f15bddefd60611c52c7","tid":1242321,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:27:14.000Z","msg":"去錯台？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T16:46:07.000Z","msg":"去錯台sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s